{"tid":2123438,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"8.3清場案 速龍稱無可能仔細記錄制伏過程 「我唔係小說家」","createTime":"2020-07-24T15:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T13:27:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"06fb851ffefa38cb6198a16289ca4df1c2e9e90f","tid":2123438,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075803&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxUad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=4457039d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075803&h=42cd2b03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075803</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）去年8月3日的「旺角再遊行」，入夜後有大批示威者於旺角區設置路障，9人被控非法集結罪，今日（24日）在九龍城裁判法院續審。負責制伏其中一名被告的「速龍」今繼續作供，他承認曾用警棍打被告。但在辯方和裁判官盤問他制伏被告的詳情時，僅稱「忘記咗」。他又被質疑庭上的作供與書面證供不符，他表示「書寫表達唔到」、「我唔係小説家，冇可能每個動作都好仔細咁寫落去。」辯方大狀笑稱他是否受文筆所限而未能在口供中詳盡地記錄，李終未有正面回應。"},{"pid":"fde32ea472d8855ebadfabb0c68a147379454696","tid":2123438,"uid":58841,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"咁後生就老人痴呆"},{"pid":"72f99e58d07b3fbe0767df8448b9ca573372cf13","tid":2123438,"uid":24788,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"要坐幾碌嫁<br />\n你估玩呀"},{"pid":"10c4000a39c7b029d23f6a47699b0f7c7d430df2","tid":2123438,"uid":72009,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"笑稱他是否受文筆所限而未能在口供中詳盡地記錄，李終未有正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時咁同笑速龍，起碼打兩棍先，現在死狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28091b40d77e1c2b3826763d2ce2be3b38fd5b7","tid":2123438,"uid":194298,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"強毅進仔所難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗打架就叻，識字唔駛做狗啦"},{"pid":